divs: sighting detailsmyself and 10 of my friends and relatives were on the back deck of my house. when i looked up and saw this violet non changing color or brightness tear drop shaped golfball sized object moving in a straight line west to east this was thursday evening at 11p.m. 6\21\12. i brought attention to the object so everyone with me would see it. seamed like 3 to 4 minutes we watched until trees hide the horizon. only 20 degrees from straight overhead north of green bay wisconsin. has anyone else seen this?
